Beáta es, * Virgo María, Dei Génitrix, quæ credidísti Dómino; perfécta sunt in te quæ dicta sunt tibi, intercéde pro nobis ad Dóminum, Deum nostrum.
Blessed art thou, * O Virgin Mary, Mother of God, that hast believed the Lord; because those things are accomplished in thee that were spoken to thee, intercede for us with the Lord our God.
